  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 160\u00b0C.",
    "Mix dark rum, coconut cream, and vanilla extract in a bowl. Set aside.",
    "In a separate bowl, combine walnuts with salt and melt butter over low heat until the mixture is golden brown.",
    "Fold melted butter mixture into the dark rum mixture.",
    "Add dark chocolate chips to the mix and stir well.",
    "Transfer mixture onto an 8x8 inch baking dish. Chill for at least 30 minutes or until firm.",
    "Cut into diamond shapes before serving."
